  "46": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: ENTERPRISE CREW FACTION: FEDERATION Montgomery Scott is the eccentric but brilliant chief engineer of the Enterprise. Though his early career suffered due to an incident involving a transporter experiment and Admiral Archer's beagle, he has gone on to see the Enterprise through thick and thin. His care has kept the ship functioning through the wear and tear of daily use and unexpected crises alike.",
  "47": "Montgomery Scott",
  "48": "SCOTTY",
  "49": "Born Engineer Scotty increases the total Hull Health of the ship by {0:0.#%} of its original Hull Health. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "50": "Born Engineer",
  "51": "+{0:#,#%} to this ship's Hull Health",
  "52": "Miracle Worker Scotty reduces the time needed to repair the ship by {0:0.#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "53": "Miracle Worker",
  "54": "+{0:#,#%} to this ship's repair speed",
