  "56": "Do not Test Me {1:#,#%} chance to Inspire Morale for one round after being hit by a critical hit Ranking Fire +{2:#,#%} to Energy Damage when the ship has Morale",
  "57": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: ENTERPRISE CREW FACTION: FEDERATION Hikaru Sulu is the helmsman of the Enterprise. Sulu's diverse skill set includes command, astrophysics, botany, and fencing; his talents have helped the crew of the Enterprise survive a variety of crises, and he has proved to be impressively intimidating in the chair.",
  "58": "Hikaru Sulu",
  "59": "SULU",
