  "62": "+{0:#,#%} to Energy Damage when the ship has Morale",
  "63": "Do not Test Me When the ship is getting hit by a Critical Hit, Sulu has a {0:0.#%} chance of inspiring Morale to the ship for one round. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "64": "Do Not Test Me",
