  "73": "+{0:#,#%} to the Shield Health of the Ship",
  "74": "Always Enthusiast When the shield is depleted, Arkady has a {0:0.#%} chance of inspiring Morale to the ship for 3 rounds. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
