  "79": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: KLINGON PATRIOTS FACTION: KLINGON EMPIRE Gorkon, an accomplished general, is respected and feared by the Klingon Empire's enemies. He is seen as a rising star in Klingon politics, and is expected to take a seat on the High Council within the decade.",
