  "101": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: KLINGON PATRIOTS FACTION: KLINGON EMPIRE Kerla is a talented military mind; though he began his career as a lowly engineering officer, his tactical skill has risen him high in Gorkon's esteem.",
