  "211": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: NERO'S CREW FACTION: ROMULAN STAR EMPIRE Vella's thirst for vengeance carried on after Nero's defeat at the hands of Kirk, Spock, and the Enterprise. Together with Arix she made her way to the Romulus of this alternate past and agreed to make use of the last speck of red matter in a bid to destroy Spock and the Enterprise.",
