  "266": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: BLOOD & HONOR FACTION: KLINGON EMPIRE Boisterous, loud, and joyful - especially in battle - Kuron is the sort of Klingon warrior that leads as much by example and inspiration as by fear and command. Kuron often sings opera during battle, punctuating his vibrato with the crashing of torpedo strikes and explosions of superheated plasma.",
