  "299": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: BLOOD & HONOR FACTION: KLINGON EMPIRE Linkasa is a prickly and cold Klingon lady; she has rebuffed the advances of her peers bloodily. She is also a capable engineer, earning glory for the Empire by keeping its fleet in good repair.",
