  "310": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: ROMULAN PATRIOTS FACTION: ROMULAN STAR EMPIRE Liviana Charvanek only recently earned her command, but has distinguished herself as a clever and ruthless strategist, and a true daughter of Romulus. While she favors to strike from positions of strength, she has earned the respect of the Klingons by her ability to fight them toe to toe.",
