  "318": "{0:#.#%} chance to cause Burning for 3 rounds when Hull Health is lower than 80%",
  "319": "Loyal Officer +{0:#.#%} Damage against battleships Resistance -{2:#.#%} to the opponent's Hull Health each turn while it is Burning vs players, and Hostiles under level 60. Most Apex Barrier resources such as Researches, Officers, Forbidden Tech, etc. will not work while Tal is appointed to the Bridge.",
