  "321": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: ROMULAN PATRIOTS FACTION: ROMULAN STAR EMPIRE Tal is Charvanek's second in command. An orderly and efficient man, he has devoted his career to supporting his captain in all her endeavors, as through her efforts, he sees a glorious future for Romulus.",
