  "332": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: ROMULAN PATRIOTS FACTION: ROMULAN STAR EMPIRE Decius has served under multiple commanders throughout his career. His friends on the senate have ensured that he finds preferable appointments; he has served repeatedly against the Klingons, and has become intimately familiar with their strengths and weaknesses.",
