  "343": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: ROMULAN PATRIOTS FACTION: ROMULAN STAR EMPIRE Mirek is Charvanek's younger sister, and a capable science officer. Her expertise is in deflection fields and radiation phenomena, and has aided her sister in tracking wilier Klingon opponents.",
