  "391": "Shady Methods",
  "392": "{0:#.#%} of the crew's Defense bonus to Shield Piercing",
  "393": "Overpower At the start of each round, if the opponent's Hull Health is under 80% of its starting total, Alexander Marcus has {0:0.#%} chance of inspiring Morale to the ship for 3 rounds. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
