  "397": "Disrupting Field -{0:#.#%} to the Shield Health of the opponent's ship each turn Romulan Grudge {2:#.#%} of the crew's Health bonus to Damage against Romulans",
  "398": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: SECTION 31 FACTION: FEDERATION Since joining Section 31, Yuki Sulu, Hikari Sulu's sister, has been involved in the management of John Harrison and an operation that resulted in a significant portion of both the Klingon Empire and the Romulan Star Empire's navies being destroyed, as well as the recovery of the last piece of red matter.",
  "399": "Yuki Sulu",
