  "509": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: MINERS & SURVEYORS FACTION: NONE Barot is a self-exiled Klingon, disinterested in warfare, honor, or most of the other trappings of Klingon society. Unsurprisingly, many Klingons treat him as a pariah, despite his numerous useful skills as a surveyor.",
  "510": "Barot",
  "511": "BAROT",
