  "531": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: SURVEYORS & MINERS FACTION: ROMULAN Domitia is an expert in astro-geology; her knowledge of asteroid mining is considerable, and she's one of the few Romulans who has worked outside of the Romulan Star Empire. She's especially interested in the Federation's approach to dilithium mining using precision phasers.",
  "532": "Domitia",
  "533": "DOMITIA",
  "534": "Hurry Home As long as the Cargo of the ship is full, Domitia increases its Warp speed by {0:0.#%}. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "535": "Hurry Home",
