  "772": "Always on Guard {1:#,#%} chance to decrease Eclipse's hostile Critical Hit Chance by 15% Intimidation +{2:#,#%} to Critical Damage against Eclipse hostiles for the first three rounds",
  "773": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: OUTLAWS FACTION: NONE A cunning, if somewhat scatterbrained member of the Outlaws crew, Sesha has spent most of her adult life being experimented on, which gave her accelerated cell regeneration. Sesha is known for her emotional intelligence, outside-the-box thinking, and a disarming personality. However, some say that her personality is a ruse, hiding a more conniving and manipulative mind underneath...",
