  "778": "Intimidation",
  "779": "+{0:#,#%} to Critical Hit Damage against Eclipse hostiles",
  "780": "Always on Guard If the opponent is an Eclipse hostile (including Armada Targets), Sesha has a {0:0.#%} chance to reduce the opponent's Critical Hit Chance by 15% Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
