  "840": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: STARFLEET ACADEMY FACTION: FEDERATION Lucia Gonzales is the easy-going leader of a troupe of the Academy's finest. Lucia specializes in diplomacy; it shows in the ease with which she appraises others and makes friends, including the frosty vulcan T'Laan and the pugnacious andorian Shev Akria.",
