  "851": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: STARFLEET ACADEMY FACTION: FEDERATION Grace Chen is a crackerjack pilot and a clever inventor. She designed and built her own leg enhancements - necessary for her to walk - and has an insatiable love for all things fast.",
