  "891": "Thorough Scans",
  "892": "+{0:#,#%} more Ship XP from battles",
  "893": "Dilithium Hunter +{0:#,#%} to Dilithium rewards from Hostiles Chirurgical Precision +{2:#,#%} to Kinetic damage against Hostiles",
  "894": "Dilithium Hunter +{0:#,#%} to Dilithium rewards from Hostiles Chirurgical Precision +{2:#,#%} to Kinetic damage against Hostiles",
  "895": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: STARFLEET ACADEMY FACTION: FEDERATION Vel K'Bentayr is a Monchezkin medical cadet; his tendency to narrate his feelings and actions in literal terms makes many think him strange, but his efficiency in diagnosing illness and emergency medical procedures earns him a lot of social leeway.",
  "896": "Vel K'Bentayr",
  "897": "VEL",
