  "943": "Resist Kinetic",
  "944": "-{0:#,#%} to Kinetic Weapon Damage from enemy player's ships",
  "945": "Battleship Specialist When inside a Battleship, Komal increases Weapon Damage against players by {0:0.#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "946": "Battleship Specialist",
  "947": "+{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage of Battleships against players",
  "948": "Interceptor Specialist +{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage of Interceptors against players Kinetic Boost +{2:#,#%} to Kinetic Weapon Damage against other player's ships",
  "949": "Interceptor Specialist +{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage of Interceptors against players Kinetic Boost +{2:#,#%} to Kinetic Weapon Damage against other player's ships",
  "950": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: GLORY IN THE KILL FACTION: KLINGON EMPIRE 'Grim' Vartoq is the sort of warrior his fellow Klingons respect but don't like to be around. Incessantly somber and spiritual, Vartoq honors his fallen foes with shouts to warn the dead and battlefield rites. He rarely partakes in bloodwine, only sings in dirges, and seems to take no joy in earning honor, just the grim satisfaction in a job well done.",
  "951": "Vartoq",
  "952": "VARTOQ",
  "953": "Kinetic Boost If the opponent is a player, Vartoq increases the damage made by the Kinetic Weapons of the ship by {0:0.#%}. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "954": "Kinetic Boost",
  "955": "+{0:#,#%} to Kinetic Weapon Damage against other player's ships",
  "956": "Interceptor Specialist When inside an Interceptor, Vartoq increases the Weapon Damage against players by {0:0.#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "957": "Interceptor Specialist",
  "958": "+{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage of Interceptors against players",
  "959": "Explorer Specialist +{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage of Explorers against players Energy Boost +{2:#,#%} to Energy Weapon Damage against other player ships",
  "960": "Explorer Specialist +{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage of Explorers against players Energy Boost +{2:#,#%} to Energy Weapon Damage against other player ships",
  "961": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: GLORY IN THE KILL FACTION: KLINGON EMPIRE Rukor is young and eager to earn fame. She is coincidentally thought of as reckless and bumbling, as her eagerness has lead her to many mistakes. Never the less, the kid is thought of as a good luck charm; the more she screws up, the more her shipmates think the next battle will turn out well.",
  "962": "Rukor",
  "963": "RUKOR",
  "964": "Energy Boost If the opponent is a player, Rukor increases the damage made by the Energy Weapons of the ship by {0:0.#%}. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "965": "Energy Boost",
  "966": "+{0:#,#%} to Energy Weapon Damage against other player ships",
  "967": "Explorer Specialist When inside an Explorer, Rukor increases the Weapon Damage against players by {0:0.#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "968": "Explorer Specialist",
  "969": "+{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage of Explorers against players",
  "970": "Motivational +{0:#,#%} to all Officer stats on the Bridge Tactician +{2:#,#%} to Weapon Damage",
  "971": "Motivational +{0:#,#%} to all Officer stats on the Bridge Tactician +{2:#,#%} to Weapon Damage",
  "972": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: ANOTHER TIME FACTION: FEDERATION Even in the Academy, Kirk showed leadership and initiative in extreme abundance. High test scores and academic performance combined with easy camaraderie allowed him to excel, despite a few stunts that put him on the instructors' radars.",
  "973": "Cadet James T. Kirk",
  "974": "CADET KIRK",
  "975": "Tactician Kirk increases the Weapon damage of the ship by {0:0.#%}. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "976": "Tactician",
  "977": "+{0:#,#%} to Weapon Damage",
  "978": "Motivational Cadet Kirk increases the Attack, Defense and Health of all Officers on the Bridge by {0:0.#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "979": "Motivational",
  "980": "+{0:#,#%} to all Officer stats on the Bridge",
  "981": "Knowledgeable +{0:#,#%} to Damage Kobayashi Maru +{2:#,#%} to Dodge, Shield Deflection and Armor",
  "982": "Knowledgeable +{0:#,#%} to Damage Kobayashi Maru +{2:#,#%} to Dodge, Shield Deflection and Armor",
  "983": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: ANOTHER TIME FACTION: FEDERATION Instructor Spock put together the Kobayashi Maru test to try and prepare cadets for the pressures and stresses of taking starships into dangerous and difficult situations. He especially wanted to stress the lesson that some situations couldn't be beaten, no matter how clever or skilled the officers in question are.",
  "984": "Instructor Spock",
  "985": "INSTR. SPOCK",
  "986": "Kobayashi Maru Instructor Spock increases the Shield Deflection, Armor and Dodge of the ship by {0:0.#%}. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "987": "Kobayashi Maru",
  "988": "+{0:#,#%} to Dodge, Shield Deflection and Armor",
  "989": "Knowledgeable Instructor Spock increases the Weapon Damage of the ship by {0:0.#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "990": "Knowledgeable",
  "991": "+{0:#,#%} to Damage",
  "992": "Doctor +{0:#,#%} to Officers Health on the ship Psychologist +{2:#,#%} to the effectiveness of the Captain Maneuver",
  "993": "Doctor +{0:#,#%} to Officers Health on the ship Psychologist +{2:#,#%} to the effectiveness of the Captain Maneuver",
  "994": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: ANOTHER TIME FACTION: FEDERATION When a bad divorce left Leonard McCoy with very little other than the clothes on his back and the bones in his body, he decided to join Starfleet and put his medical expertise to good use. He rapidly befriended James Kirk, and the two stuck together throughout their years at the Academy.",
  "995": "Cadet Leonard McCoy",
  "996": "CADET MCCOY",
  "997": "Psychologist During combat, Cadet McCoy increases the effectiveness of the Captain Maneuver by {0:0.#%}. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "998": "Psychologist",
  "999": "+{0:#,#%} to the effectiveness of the Captain Maneuver",
  "1000": "Doctor Cadet McCoy increases the Health of all Officers on the ship by {0:0.#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "1001": "Doctor",
  "1002": "+{0:#,#%} to Officers Health on the ship",
  "1003": "Sturdy Ship +{0:#,#%} to Hull Health Warp Theory +{2:#} Warp Distance",
  "1004": "Sturdy Ship +{0:#,#%} to Hull Health Warp Theory +{2:#} Warp Distance",
  "1005": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: ANOTHER TIME FACTION: FEDERATION Montgomery Scott's time in the Academy was punctuated by successes and failures in equal measure, most notably his attempt to prove that transporter range could be extended to cover an entire star system. His test subject, Admiral Archer's prize beagle, never re-materialized.",
  "1006": "Cadet Montgomery Scott",
  "1007": "CADET SCOTTY",
