  "1123": "Resistance is Futile When fighting a Borg Tactical Probe, Seven of Eleven has a {0:0.#%} chance of increasing the number of shots of each weapon by 2. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "1124": "Resistance is Futile",
  "1125": "{1:#,#%} chance of adding 2 shots to each weapon when fighting Borg Tactical Probes",
  "1126": "Fight the Collective +{0:#,#%} to Critical Hit Chance against Borg ships Cybernetic Enhancements +{2:#,#%} to the Attack of all Officers on the ship",
  "1127": "Fight the Collective +{0:#,#%} to Critical Hit Chance against Borg ships Cybernetic Enhancements +{2:#,#%} to the Attack of all Officers on the ship",
  "1128": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: UNIMATRIX TWELVE FACTION: NONE During the Borg onslaught, Azetbur took it upon herself to covertly enter Borg-occupied space in an attempt to study and understand this dangerous new enemy. Unfortunately, her curiosity would prove treacherous, as she was quickly captured and assimilated into the Collective. Where Azetbur, daughter of Gorkon, of the House of Makok once stood, there now remains only Eight of Eleven. Tormented by the loss of his daughter to the Borg Collective, Chancellor Gorkon will stop at nothing until she is returned to her former self.",
  "1129": "Eight of Eleven",
