  "1135": "Fight the Collective",
  "1136": "+{0:#,#%} to Critical Hit Chance against Borg ships",
  "1137": "Borg Polarization -{0:#,#%} to opponent Borg Critical Hit Chance Adapt & Overcome +{2:#,#%} to the Defense of all Officers on the Ship",
  "1138": "Borg Polarization -{0:#,#%} to opponent Borg Critical Hit Chance Adapt & Overcome +{2:#,#%} to the Defense of all Officers on the Ship",
  "1139": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: UNIMATRIX TWELVE FACTION: NONE When the USS Sterling went missing in action at the borders of Borg-occupied space, Cadet Gonzales was among the first crew assigned to investigate the ship’s disappearance. However, it was not long before members of this search party were greeted with the same fate as the Sterling’s crew - a forced, painful assimilation into the Borg Collective. Lucia Gonzales is dead. All that remains is Nine of Eleven, Septenary Adjunct of Unimatrix Twelve.",
