  "1256": "Hold Position",
  "1257": "+{0:#,#%} to all Officers Attack when the ship defends a Capture Node",
  "1258": "Protective {0:#,#%} of Health to Armor when defending on a Capture Node Learned from the Best +{2:#,#%} to Jumping and Summoning Cost Efficiency",
  "1259": "Protective {0:#,#%} of Health to Armor when defending on a Capture Node Learned from the Best +{2:#,#%} to Jumping and Summoning Cost Efficiency",
  "1260": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: DISCOVERY FACTION: FEDERATION Empathy. Compassion. Integrity. Three qualities every good doctor should hold. When it comes to Dr. Hugh Culber, however, he doesn’t just uphold these qualities... He exemplifies them. Hugh decided to enrol in medical school after a chance meeting with an impressive doctor after a hiking accident. He excelled immediately, graduating top of his class. During the Human-Klingon war of 2256, Culber served onboard the USS Discovery as its chief medical officer. He served with his husband, Paul Stamets and was known as a man with unwavering integrity and an iron will.",
  "1261": "Hugh Culber",
  "1262": "CULBER",
