  "1267": "Protective",
  "1268": "{0:#,#%} of Health to Armor when defending on a Capture Node",
  "1269": "Isogen Miner +{0:#,#%} to Isogen Mining Speed Cybernetic Tactician +{3:#,#%} chance to inflict Burning when defending on a Node",
  "1270": "Isogen Miner +{0:#,#%} to Isogen Mining Speed Cybernetic Tactician +{3:#,#%} chance to inflict Burning when defending on a Node",
  "1271": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: DISCOVERY FACTION: FEDERATION Horribly wounded in a tragic shuttle accident, Lieutenant Airiam was saved by an experimental procedure. Following the aftermath of the accident, Airiam received cybernetic augmentations. These enhanced her senses, allowed her to make complex decisions in nano-seconds and improved her physical strength and agility. These upgrades, along with her intelligence and courage, made her a natural fit for the bridge of the USS Discovery. It was not long before Airiam rose up the ranks of Starfleet, eventually achieving the rank of Lieutenant Commander. Though her past will always be shadowed by her tragedy, Airiam’s future remains bright.",
  "1272": "Airiam",
  "1273": "AIRIAM",
  "1274": "Cybernetic Tactician When defending on a Capture Node, at the start of each round, Airiam has a {0:#.#%} chance of Burning the opponent for this round. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
