  "1292": "Ruthlessness {0:#,#%} of Defense to Piercing if the opponent has a Hull Breach when attacking on a capture node Sadistic {2:#,#%} of Health to Mitigation if the opponent has a Hull Breach",
  "1293": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: TERRAN EMPIRE FACTION: NONE Unlike her USS Discovery counterpart, Captain Tilly is charismatic, ruthless, and bloodthirsty. Leaving a trail of destruction in her wake in any system she targets, her reputation has garnered her several nicknames, including “The Slayer of Sorna Prime”, “The Witch of Wurna Minor\", and “Captain Killy” – each of which she relishes.",
