  "1299": "Ruthlessness When attacking on a capture node, at the start of each turn, as long as the opponent's ship has a Hull Breach, Captain Tilly increases the Armor Piercing, Shield Piercing and Accuracy of the ship by {0:0.#%} of the total Defense of all Officers on the ship (cumulative). Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
