  "1465": "+{0:#,#%} to all Mitigation stats when fighting Hostiles/Armadas",
  "1466": "First, Do No Harm When fighting Hostiles and Armadas, Beverly Crusher restores Shield Health each round equal to {0:0.#%} of the Health of all Officers on the ship. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
