  "1564": "+{0:#,#%} to Crit Chance against players for the first 8 rounds of combat",
  "1565": "Soldier of the Empire When fighting other players, Honorguard Worf increases the ship's Armor Piercing by {0:0.#%} of Crew Attack whenever the ship scores a critical hit. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
