  "1886": "{1:#,#%} chance of Burning player ships for 3 rounds per hit if on a Battleship.",
  "1887": "Targeting Optimization While on a Battleship fighting a Burning player ship, at the start of each round Strike Team SNW La'an increases the number of shots per Weapon by {0:#,#%}. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "1888": "Targeting Optimization",
  "1889": "+{0:#,#%} to Weapon Shots on round start if on a Battleship fighting Burning player ships.",
