  "1989": "Dominion Collaborator While on an Interceptor fighting a player ship with Hull Breach, if Damar scores a Critical Hit, increase Critical Hit Chance by {0:#,#%} once per Weapon for the remainder of battle. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
  "1990": "Dominion Collaborator",
  "1991": "Damar's Interceptor gets +{0:#,#%} to Crit Chance for each Crit made on player ships with Hull Breach.",
  "1992": "Silver Tongue On round start, Weyoun has a {1:#,#%} chance to apply Morale for 3 rounds when fighting against players, if on an Explorer. Manipulate, Cajole, Deceive Increases Weapon Shots by +{2:#,#%} at the start of each Round for 2 Rounds when fighting players, if on an Explorer with Morale.",
  "1993": "Silver Tongue {1:#,#%} chance to apply Morale for 3 Rounds on combat start when fighting against players, if on an Explorer. Manipulate, Cajole, Deceive Increases Weapon Shots by +{2:#,#%} at the start of each Round for 2 Rounds when fighting players, if on an Explorer with Morale.",
  "1994": "CLASS: COMMAND GROUP: DEEP SPACE NINE FACTION: DOMINION What is the true measure of loyalty? Some might say it lies in unending devotion, until one’s own demise. If this is the case, Weyoun has proven his loyalty several times over. Like all the Vorta, the self-described “emissaries” of the Dominion, Weyoun, as we know him, is a clone. The original Weyoun is long dead, though his undying devotion to the Dominion can be seen in his successors, each of them bringing a new improvement to the line of Weyouns, a new mark on their noble progenitor’s legacy. Despite minor differences in personality, each Weyoun shares some common traits. He is a shrewd politician and a relentless negotiator. He will stop at nothing to ensure the Founders’ will is done, regardless of the cost.",
  "1995": "Weyoun",
  "1996": "WEYOUN",
  "1997": "Manipulate, Cajole, Deceive Weyoun increases Weapon Shots by +{0:#,#%} at the start of each Round for 2 Rounds when fighting players, if on an Explorer with Morale. Captain Maneuvers are activated when an officer is captain of a ship.",
