  "2014": "Lost in Translation {1:#,#%} chance at the start of combat to delay opponent weapons for 3 Rounds when attacked by players, if your ship is an Explorer. Breen Served Cold Decreases opponent Critical Chance by -{2:#,#%} at the start of each Round for 3 Rounds while fighting players, if on an Explorer with Morale.",
  "2015": "Lost in Translation {1:#,#%} chance at the start of combat to delay opponent Weapons for 3 Rounds while fighting players, if on an Explorer. Breen Served Cold Decreases opponent Critical Chance by -{2:#,#%} at the start of each Round for 3 Rounds while fighting players, if on an Explorer with Morale.",
  "2016": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: DEEP SPACE NINE FACTION: DOMINION Few species in the Alpha Quadrant are as mysterious, as entirely unplaceable, as the Breen. In their eerie refrigeration suits, the Breen’s soldiers take on an almost supernatural visage, an image of alien invaders from old Earth holotapes. What little is known about the Breen tells us that they are ruthless in combat, and boast some of the most powerful ships in the quadrant. The secret to their power is unknown, but we can be sure that to rise the ranks in the Breen military requires cunning, unmatched skill and unwavering ruthlessness.",
  "2017": "Pon",
  "2018": "PON",
  "2019": "Breen Served Cold Pon decreases opponent player's Critical Chance by {0:0.#%} at the start of each Round for 3 Rounds if on an Explorer with Morale. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
