  "2140": "Not Perceived as a Threat",
  "2141": "No effect.",
  "2142": "Adapt and Assimilate At the start of each round, if opponents Hull health is below 95%, Dezoc has {0:#,#%} chance to apply Assimilate to it for 4 rounds. While a ship is affected by the Assimilate state, Officer Abilities have their effectiveness reduced by 25%. Below-Decks Abilities are only activated when assigned to a below-decks slot on a ship.",
  "2143": "Adapt and Assimilate",
  "2144": "{1:#,#%} chance of applying Assimilate to opponents with less than 95% Hull Health each Round for 4 rounds.",
  "2145": "Not Perceived as a Threat This Captain's Maneuver has no effect. Programmed to Evolve -{2:#,#%} Critical Damage dealt by Borg Solo Armadas when fighting them each round for 1 round. Closer to Perfection {4:#,#%} to Armor, Shield Deflection and Dodge each round if fighting player ships with Assimilate.",
  "2146": "Not Perceived as a Threat This Captain's Maneuver has no effect. Programmed to Evolve -{2:#,#%} Critical Damage dealt by Borg Solo Armadas when fighting them each round for 1 round. Closer to Perfection {4:#,#%} to Armor, Shield Deflection and Dodge each round if fighting player ships with Assimilate.",
  "2147": "CLASS: ENGINEERING GROUP: UNIMATRIX TWELVE FACTION: BORG Known to the Collective as Species 180, Ferengi care only about their own profit, but what happens when individuality, the basis of their business practice, is taken away? You get an extremely effective Borg drone, intelligent and skilled in engineering, trade, resources and sciences. Gossa was an exceptional businessman, conducting deals of all sizes across the Alpha Quadrant, but his luck soon ran out. While transporting modified photon torpedoes to a Romulan officer, Gossa crossed paths with the Borg Cube. This was the first and the last time his negotiating skills had no effect.",
  "2148": "Gossa",
  "2149": "GOSSA",
  "2150": "Programmed to Evolve When fighting against a Borg Solo Armada, at the start of each round reduce target's Critical Damage by {0:#,#%} for 1 round. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "2151": "Programmed to Evolve",
  "2152": "-{0:#,#%} Critical Damage dealt by Borg Solo Armadas when fighting them each round for 1 round.",
