  "2274": "War's Almost Over At the start of combat against non-Player hostiles or Armadas, Tom Paris increases your Armor, Shield Deflection, and Dodge by {0:0.#%} of Defense. Below-Decks Abilities are only activated when assigned to a below-decks slot on a ship.",
  "2275": "War's Almost Over",
  "2276": "Increase your Armor, Shield Deflection, and Dodge by {0:#,#%} of Defense at the start of combat.",
  "2277": "Unfit To Lead This Captain's Maneuver has no effect. Are We Friends? Harry Kim increases all positive Reputation gains by +{2:#,#%}. To the Journey! At the start of a round, Harry Kim has a {5:#,#%} chance to apply Morale to your ship when fighting non-Player hostiles and Armadas for 1 round.",
  "2278": "Unfit To Lead This Captain's Maneuver has no effect. Are We Friends? Harry Kim increases all positive Reputation gains by +{2:#,#%}. To the Journey! At the start of a round, Harry Kim has a {5:#,#%} chance to apply Morale to your ship when fighting non-Player hostiles and Armadas for 1 round.",
  "2279": "CLASS: SCIENCE GROUP: VOYAGER FACTION: FEDERATION Life frequently finds a way of providing opportunities to pursue our ambitions through unlikely means. For Ensign Harry Kim and his desires to explore the Galaxy and beyond, there would be no exception to this rule. Throughout his time in the Academy, Kim displayed all the hallmarks of a promising career in Starfleet, demonstrating exceptional skills in the fields of analytical operations and engineering. However, when Kim was handed his first assignment as operations officer aboard the Intrepid-class USS Voyager, his aspiration to explore the cosmos would be achieved in the most unimaginable way possible. Stranded almost 70,000 lightyears from home, Kim was about to embark on a journey that few have ever undertaken. Although wounded by his stranding far from loved ones back home, Kim found solace among his colleagues on the decks of the USS Voyager. With the help of his newfound friends, this promising young Ensign will inevitably understand that when it comes to the voyage home, it’s not the destination that matters, but the journey itself.",
  "2280": "Harry Kim",
  "2281": "HARRY KIM",
  "2282": "Are We Friends? Harry Kim increases all positive Reputation gains by {0:0.#%}. Officer Abilities are activated when assigned to the bridge of a ship.",
  "2283": "Are We Friends?",
  "2284": "Increases all positive Reputation gains by {0:#,#%}.",
