  "2788": "Chain of Command This Officer does not have a Captain's Maneuver. Equipping this Officer as the captain of a ship provides no benefit. The Looking Glass Decreases all Armada and Invading Entities base mitigation stats by {2:#,#%} of total Officer Defense every round (Cumulative) Too Hot to Handle Increases base warp speed by {4:#,#%}",
