  "3185": "SNW T'Pring Increases the amount of 3⇵-6⇵ Ore/Crystal/Gas collected by {0:#.#%} ({1:#,#%} at rank {2:#,#}), without draining the mining node faster. Below-Deck Abilities are only activated when assigned to a below-decks slot on a ship.",
  "3186": "Logic Dictates",
